# M6 countdown-fix — host side. Counts down 3 → 2 → 1 → GO! over a
# full 3 s window (was 1 s default). Burst captures the entire arc
# so the side-by-side output can prove host + client see the same
# integer at the same tick (within snapshot quant).
#
# Auto_start_seconds defaults to 1s in shot mode → COUNTDOWN starts
# around t=60. With countdown_seconds 3 it runs to ~t=240. GO!
# splash lingers ~36 ticks past phase flip.

window 1280 720
out build/shots/net/cd_host
network host 24031
name HostA
loadout - "Pulse Rifle" "Sidearm" Light Standard
map slipstream
no_parallax
countdown_seconds 3

burst t from 60 to 290 every 10
contact_sheet sheet cols 6 cell 320 180

at 320 end
